text: Ledina is a dispersed settlement in the hills northwest of Sevnica in east- central Slovenia. It is also a given name. It may refer to: *Ledina Aliolli, Albanian politician and member of the Assembly of the Republic of Albania *Ledina Çelo (born 1977), Albanian singer and model *Ledina Mandia, Albanian politician, Albanian Deputy Prime Minister
title: Ledina (disambiguation)
